<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">End with a challenge to take action. Choose a closing question to help each person identify their next steps.</p>

<ul>
  <li>What one step could you take to chase the light and defeat greed this week?</li>
  <li>Keep each other accountable to give daily this week. Tip better, pay for people behind you, and care for people in need.</li>
